<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
   <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8" />
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
      <title>Statistics - Second Exam (Coming Soon)</title>
      <link
         href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap"
         rel="stylesheet"
      />
      <style>
         :root {
            --primary-color: #3b82f6;
            --secondary-color: #2563eb;
            --background-color: #e8e8e8;
            --text-color: #1e293b;
            --card-background: #ffffff;
         }

         * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
         }

         body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
         }

         .container {
            background-color: var(--card-background);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
         }

         @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
               opacity: 0;
               transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
               opacity: 1;
               transform: translateY(0);
            }
         }

         .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
         }

         h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
         }

         h2 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
         }

         p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0.9;
         }

         .coming-soon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin: 40px 0;
         }

         .notify-button {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
         }

         .notify-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
         }

         .notify-button:focus {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
         }

         @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
               padding: 30px;
               width: 90%;
            }
            h1 {
               font-size: 2rem;
            }
            h2 {
               font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .coming-soon {
               font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
         }

         .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
         }

         .logo-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
         }

         .logo-link:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
         }

         .logo-image {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin-right: 10px;
         }

         .company-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
         }

         @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .logo-image {
               width: 50px;
               height: 50px;
            }
            .company-name {
               font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
         }
      </style>
   </head>
   <body>
      <div class="container">
         <div class="logo-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo-link">
               <img
                  src="/sprites/logo.ico"
                  alt="Stat&Mat Logo"
                  class="logo-image"
               />
               <span class="company-name">Stat&Mat</span>
            </a>
         </div>
         <h1>Statistics - Second Exam</h1>

         <p class="coming-soon">Coming soon!</p>

         <p>
            We are preparing comprehensive learning materials to help you master
            the topics and prepare for the second statistics exam. Stay tuned!
         </p>

         <h2>What to expect?</h2>
         <p>
            Detailed video lessons, worked examples, and interactive exercises
            designed to help you confidently master the material for the second
            statistics exam.
         </p>
         <p>
            Be among the first to know when the content goes live. Sign up for
            notifications to get early access!
         </p>

         <button type="submit" class="notify-button">Notify Me</button>
      </div>
   </body>
</html>
